Steps to Create HTML Report

1. Run the the test you want to get report about if you haven't run yet

2. Click on Run -> Edit Configuration

3. Find the name of the test you want to get report about.

4. On the right hand side click on Listeners button

5. Click on add button below Listeners

6. Search for report and choose EmailableReporter

7. Click on Apply then OK

8. Run your test again